==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from German, meaning "play of bells"

===Noun===
'''glockenspiel'''

#''Music.'' A musical instrument in the percussion family of instruments, similar to a xylophone, in that it has tuned bars laid out in a piano-keyboard-like fashion, but is much smaller in size and much higher in pitch.

